<script language="javascript">
    function processRvpSelection(origCuid) {
        var form     = document.RvpSelection;
        var rdd      = form.RvpDropdown;
        var rddIndex = rdd.selectedIndex;
        var rddValue = rdd.options[rddIndex].value;
        
        if (rddValue.length &gt; 0) {
            form.origCuid.value  = origCuid;
            // Delegation Enabled -- Set to origCuid to disable delegation
            //form.cuid.value     = origCuid;
            form.cuid.value     = rddValue;
            form.rv.value       = rddValue;	            
            form.submit();
        }
    }

     function changeRepresentingAs() {

                  
			var form     = document.RvpSelection;
			var newCuid = form.cuidEnter.value;
			if(newCuid != null &amp;&amp; newCuid != "")
			 {
				form.cuid.value     = newCuid;
				form.rv.value       = newCuid;
                         
				form.submit();
			 }
			 else
			{
				 alert("Please enter some cuid value in the text box before pressing enter.");
			 }
    }

    function entsub(myform) 
        {		
           if (window.event &amp;&amp; window.event.keyCode == 13) 
               changeRepresentingAs();
           else return true;
        }


    function processViewAsSelection(cuid, origCuid) {
        var form      = document.ViewAsSelection;
        var vadd      = form.ViewAsDropdown;
        var vaddIndex = vadd.selectedIndex;
        var vaddValue = vadd.options[vaddIndex].value;
        var delimIdx  = vaddValue.indexOf('%');
        var rform     = document.RvpSelection;
        var rddValue  = "";
        if (rform != null) {
            var rdd      = rform.RvpDropdown;
            var rddIndex = rdd.selectedIndex;
            rddValue     = rdd.options[rddIndex].value;
        }
        if (delimIdx != -1) {
            var salesIds        = vaddValue.substring(0, delimIdx);
            var role            = vaddValue.substring(delimIdx+1, vaddValue.length);
            form.salesIds.value = salesIds;
            form.role.value     = role;
            form.origCuid.value  = origCuid;
            form.cuid.value     = cuid;
            form.rv.value       = rddValue;
            form.sv.value       = vaddValue;
            form.submit();
        }
    }
</script>
